T1  - The Role of Risk Sharing and Risk Taking Under Gainsharing.
AU  - Gomez-Mejia, Luis R.
AU  - Welbourne, Thereas M.
AU  - Wiseman, Robert M.
Y1  - 2000/07/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.2000.3363318
